                <strong>Framer:</strong> 2/15 people said "this looks like a template"
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Durable's layouts are locked. You can change colors and images, but the structure screams "AI generated." Framer lets you break the grid, adjust spacing, and make it feel custom.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="bg-red-100 rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-red-600 font-black text-xl">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Design Flexibility</p>
